I was invited to do a blog post as one in a collection of responses to an article The Atlantic published in September 2012. The article was by Peg Tyre, and it was entitled &quot;Why Students Can't Write&quot; 

My piece was entitled, &quot;Are We Learning the Right Lessons from New Dorp High School.&quot;

Here is the link: http://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2012/09/are-we-learning-the-right-lessons-from-new-dorp-high-school/263010/
